  "root_text": {
    "sn21.12:0.1": "Saṁyutta Nikāya 21.12 ",
    "sn21.12:0.2": "1. Bhikkhuvagga ",
    "sn21.12:0.3": "Sahāyakasutta ",
    "sn21.12:1.1": "Sāvatthiyaṁ viharati. ",
    "sn21.12:1.2": "Atha kho dve bhikkhū sahāyakā āyasmato mahākappinassa saddhivihārino yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkamiṁsu. ",
    "sn21.12:1.3": "Addasā kho bhagavā te bhikkhū dūratova āgacchante. ",
    "sn21.12:1.4": "Disvāna bhikkhū āmantesi: ",
    "sn21.12:1.5": "“passatha no tumhe, bhikkhave, ete bhikkhū sahāyake āgacchante kappinassa saddhivihārino”ti? ",
    "sn21.12:1.6": "“Evaṁ, bhante”. ",
    "sn21.12:1.7": "“Ete kho te bhikkhū mahiddhikā mahānubhāvā. ",
    "sn21.12:1.8": "Na ca sā samāpatti sulabharūpā, yā tehi bhikkhūhi asamāpannapubbā. ",
    "sn21.12:1.9": "Yassa catthāya kulaputtā sammadeva agārasmā anagāriyaṁ pabbajanti tadanuttaraṁ brahmacariyapariyosānaṁ diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṁ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja viharantī”ti. ",
    "sn21.12:2.1": "Idamavoca bhagavā. ",
    "sn21.12:2.2": "Idaṁ vatvāna sugato athāparaṁ etadavoca satthā: ",
    "sn21.12:3.1": "“Sahāyāvatime bhikkhū, ",
    "sn21.12:3.2": "cirarattaṁ sametikā; ",
    "sn21.12:3.3": "Sameti nesaṁ saddhammo, ",
    "sn21.12:3.4": "dhamme buddhappavedite. ",
    "sn21.12:4.1": "Suvinītā kappinena, ",
    "sn21.12:4.2": "dhamme ariyappavedite; ",
    "sn21.12:4.3": "Dhārenti antimaṁ dehaṁ, ",
    "sn21.12:4.4": "jetvā māraṁ savāhinin”ti. ",
    "sn21.12:4.5": "Dvādasamaṁ. ",
    "sn21.12:4.6": "Bhikkhuvaggo paṭhamo. ",
    "sn21.12:5.0": "Tassuddānaṁ ",
    "sn21.12:5.1": "Kolito upatisso ca, ",
    "sn21.12:5.2": "ghaṭo cāpi pavuccati; ",
    "sn21.12:5.3": "Navo sujāto bhaddi ca, ",
    "sn21.12:5.4": "visākho nando tisso ca; ",
    "sn21.12:5.5": "Theranāmo ca kappino, ",
    "sn21.12:5.6": "sahāyena ca dvādasāti. ",
    "sn21.12:5.7": "Bhikkhusaṁyuttaṁ samattaṁ. ",
    "sn21.12:5.8": "Nidānavaggo dutiyo. ",
    "sn21.12:6.0": "Tassuddānaṁ ",
    "sn21.12:6.1": "Nidānābhisamayadhātu, ",
    "sn21.12:6.2": "anamataggena kassapaṁ; ",
    "sn21.12:6.3": "Sakkārarāhulalakkhaṇo, ",
    "sn21.12:6.4": "opammabhikkhunā vaggo. ",
    "sn21.12:6.5": "Dutiyo tena pavuccatīti. ",
    "sn21.12:6.6": "Nidānavaggasaṁyuttapāḷi niṭṭhitā. "
  },
  "translation_text": {
    "sn21.12:0.1": "Linked Discourses 21.12 ",
    "sn21.12:0.2": "1. Monks ",
    "sn21.12:0.3": "Companions ",
    "sn21.12:1.1": "At Sāvatthī. ",
    "sn21.12:1.2": "Then two mendicants who were companions, protégés of Venerable Mahākappina, went to see the Buddha. ",
    "sn21.12:1.3": "The Buddha saw them coming off in the distance, ",
    "sn21.12:1.4": "and addressed the mendicants: ",
    "sn21.12:1.5": "“Mendicants, do you see those monks coming who are companions, protégés of Venerable Mahākappina?” ",
    "sn21.12:1.6": "“Yes, sir.” ",
    "sn21.12:1.7": "“Those mendicants are very mighty and powerful. ",
    "sn21.12:1.8": "It’s not easy to find an attainment that they have not already attained. ",
    "sn21.12:1.9": "And they’ve realized the supreme end of the spiritual path in this very life. They live having achieved with their own insight the goal for which gentlemen rightly go forth from the lay life to homelessness.” ",
    "sn21.12:2.1": "That is what the Buddha said. ",
    "sn21.12:2.2": "Then the Holy One, the Teacher, went on to say: ",
    "sn21.12:3.1": "“These companion mendicants ",
    "sn21.12:3.2": "have been together for a long time. ",
    "sn21.12:3.3": "The true teaching has brought them together, ",
    "sn21.12:3.4": "the teaching proclaimed by the Buddha. ",
    "sn21.12:4.1": "They’ve been well trained by Kappina ",
    "sn21.12:4.2": "in the teaching proclaimed by the Noble One. ",
    "sn21.12:4.3": "They bear their final body, ",
    "sn21.12:4.4": "having vanquished Māra with his legions.” ",
    "sn21.12:4.5": "",
    "sn21.12:4.6": "",
    "sn21.12:5.1": "",
    "sn21.12:5.2": "",
    "sn21.12:5.3": "",
    "sn21.12:5.4": "",
    "sn21.12:5.5": "",
    "sn21.12:5.6": "",
    "sn21.12:5.7": "The Linked Discourses on monks are complete. ",
    "sn21.12:5.8": "",
    "sn21.12:6.1": "",
    "sn21.12:6.2": "",
    "sn21.12:6.3": "",
    "sn21.12:6.4": "",
    "sn21.12:6.5": "",
    "sn21.12:6.6": "The Book of Causality is finished. "
  },
